{"tid":1994024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭抗疫成功，民意開始逆轉","createTime":"2020-04-29T07:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T10:47:15.000Z","uid":24306,"like":10,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8bf0afc9c4fd0dfabf092f3d9f0d8bdfc186b5fb","tid":1994024,"uid":24306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />身邊d人話林鄭今次做得好<br />\n黑警已經殺緊曱甴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地仲鬥緊黃，派口罩比藍屍"},{"pid":"eeea673caa6030e8480ad6f817f978f68bf53770","tid":1994024,"uid":268516,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:46:16.000Z","msg":"但啲錢仲未到手"},{"pid":"407b17c90956df89f5b1a3aaf8c1db637440cf16","tid":1994024,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:50:33.000Z","msg":"港共收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n支持手足<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-------<br />\n<br />\n【打柒支那01】共派政黨民建聯得分上升8% 黨媒01是背後元兇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1993353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1993353</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家係咪已經受夠01滲透連登亂鳩咁帶風向呢？<br />\n唔該你哋班連登仔唔撚好再share 01 news，唔好再被佢帶風向<br />\n搞鳩我哋香港人咁撚耐 支那01呢條數香港人未同你計 <br />\n一定要打撚柒支那01<br />\n<br />\n2019.10.06 曲解個別人士看法 為連登仔「主流」意見<br />\n不排除發表裝修過火言論人士係01自己友裡應外合 <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3372054/org/275d81f556563cc11f7f4df5bd1b3a68.jpg/ZNGnljnlcF3bfZKzYGOuq1MS4Xzj4awRMtY9gTLWPYE?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3372054%2Forg%2F275d81f556563cc11f7f4df5bd1b3a68.jpg%2FZNGnljnlcF3bfZKzYGOuq1MS4Xzj4awRMtY9gTLWPYE%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=7861ddf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019.09.22 試圖用煽情手段令人對示威者反感<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3317339/org/21f8e8c12ac3ac88cdc4ad6d7d99f723.jpg/AT1fGhI0UWexOIYV9dBE_Of_yZ-j--bEbklny25JZ8s?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3317339%2Forg%2F21f8e8c12ac3ac88cdc4ad6d7d99f723.jpg%2FAT1fGhI0UWexOIYV9dBE_Of_yZ-j--bEbklny25JZ8s%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=6fda6241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那01最近已經現撚晒形，直頭唔同你扮<br />\n2020.04.27 合理化中聯辦港澳辦在港干預內部事務 爭取政治話語權行為<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200427/331515838307897345.jpeg/xDRqAvnvB84AtlSIOBccWOQrCm3_BnxUKz52rSs-dq0?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200427%2F331515838307897345.jpeg%2FxDRqAvnvB84AtlSIOBccWOQrCm3_BnxUKz52rSs-dq0%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=bdd570dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2020.04.25 口罩問題拖慢嚟處理 港共遲遲唔封關 要手足炸羅湖關口 醫護罷工先肯「局部封鎖」，如果咁樣都唔慢點樣先算慢？？？<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200425/330700382865068033.jpeg/dVvhHBAxURJ0q55foYVsUOigJsUP_8ZdPbyKZz28imc?v=w480r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200425%2F330700382865068033.jpeg%2FdVvhHBAxURJ0q55foYVsUOigJsUP_8ZdPbyKZz28imc%3Fv%3Dw480r16_9&h=ee7057e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近搭車，仲係見到好多港豬攞住手機睇01，此風不可長！！！<br />\n支那01最近仲成為咗網上媒體market share第一，01笑緊你哋班港豬同連燈仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4384168/org/8c15ee579b80fc401ab1007b7e6688a1.jpg/RBgNUKrwXNjia4szpNiqu7ZA6PHA5gHvAEV_ugBFf7o?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4384168%2Forg%2F8c15ee579b80fc401ab1007b7e6688a1.jpg%2FRBgNUKrwXNjia4szpNiqu7ZA6PHA5gHvAEV_ugBFf7o%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=aad31c13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次區議會，單議席單票制，唔駛配票，我哋都贏得好險<br />\n今次立法會，比例代表制，配票更加複雜，加上對家機器全開，要贏難度更高<br />\n今次一輸，香港人有心理準備未來20-30年要返去極權蘇聯統治下嘅東歐模式<br />\n唔好唔記得上年區議會選舉前一日係自己個「01觀點」度寫咗啲咩<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/hk01-13_sJn01_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fhk01-13_sJn01_1200x0.png&h=0c6e51b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只要支那01攞到大約5-10%中間淺黃淺藍民意，立法會選舉可以係死得人<br />\n為咗香港未來，一定要做啲嘢<br />\n支那01，一定要打撚柒佢，一定要打撚柒支那01<br />\n<br />\n對付方式<br />\n支那01廣告收入相對無CCTVB或者東方咁多，因為呢個係于品海賣港賊，背後一堆共派資本控制同泵水<br />\n如果有安裝支那01app，記得剷撚走佢，剷完之後，裝返立場新聞，可以嘅話最好訂埋蘋果日報，人哋而家告急緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外誠心推介：<br />\n大紀元時報，出文量極度頻密，香港嘢跟得好貼<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2F&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=7afd6db2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/</a><br />\n眾新聞，由資深傳媒人創立<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2F&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=a196b499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/</a><br />\n香港新聞 | NEWSHK24<br />\n<a href=\"https://newshk24.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewshk24.com%2F&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=b4b7d27c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newshk24.com/</a><br />\n本土新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.localpresshk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=88f8da6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.localpresshk.com/</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogle新聞News Feed，如果見到01啲新聞彈出嚟，記得取消追蹤！<br />\n自己做完之後，記得幫自己屋企人做，做完之後幫朋友做<br />\n一傳十，十傳百，發揮群眾力量<br />\n一定要打撚柒支那01<br />\n<br />\n唔該你哋班連登仔唔撚好再share 01 news<br />\n唔該你哋班連登仔唔撚好再share 01 news<br />\n唔該你哋班連登仔唔撚好再share 01 news<br />\n因為好重要 所以要講三次<br />\n<br />\n支那01，一定要打撚柒佢<br />\n守護香港，反對紅媒滲透"},{"pid":"9fc41c93d88041ca8a8ee47b8798f0da502343a5